---
const siteName = "FLY Unlimited";
const contactEmail = "hello@fly-unlimited.com"; // change if needed
const appStoreUrl = "#";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>How it works • {siteName}</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="How FLY works — create a FLY, run it in LiveTime, add proof, submit. Clean and simple."
    />

    <style>
      :root{
        --bg:#ffffff;
        --text:#0b0c10;
        --muted:rgba(11,12,16,.62);
        --soft:rgba(11,12,16,.04);
        --hair:rgba(11,12,16,.10);
        --hairStrong:rgba(11,12,16,.14);

        --max:1120px;

        --rXL: 34px;
        --rL: 28px;
        --rM: 22px;

        --ease: cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1);
      }

      *{ box-sizing:border-box; }
      html,body{ margin:0; padding:0; }
      body{
        font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
        line-height: 1.25;
      }

      a{ color:inherit; text-decoration:none; }
      a:focus-visible{
        outline: 3px solid rgba(0,0,0,.16);
        outline-offset: 3px;
        border-radius: 12px;
      }

      /* ===== Top nav ===== */
      .topbar{
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 50;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,.96);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      }
      .topbarInner{
        max-width: var(--max);
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 10px 18px;
        display:flex;
        align-items:center;
        justify-content:space-between;
        gap: 14px;
      }
      .brand{
        display:flex;
        align-items:center;
        gap:10px;
        min-height:44px;
      }
      .mascot{
        width:26px;
        height:26px;
        border-radius:10px;
        object-fit:contain;
        display:block;
      }

      .nav{
        display:flex;
        align-items:center;
        gap:10px;
      }
      .navBtn{
        width:42px;
        height:42px;
        display:grid;
        place-items:center;
        border-radius:999px;
        color: rgba(11,12,16,.70);
        transition: background .18s var(--ease), color .18s var(--ease);
      }
      .navBtn:hover{
        background: rgba(0,0,0,.05);
        color: rgba(11,12,16,.92);
      }
      .navBtn.active{
        background: rgba(0,0,0,.08);
        color: rgba(11,12,16,.96);
      }
      .navBtn svg{
        width:18px;
        height:18px;
        stroke: currentColor;
        stroke-width:2.2;
        fill:none;
        stroke-linecap:round;
        stroke-linejoin:round;
      }
      .navIcon{
        width:18px;
        height:18px;
        display:block;
        object-fit:contain;
      }

      /* ===== Layout ===== */
      .wrap{
        max-width: var(--max);
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 18px;
      }

      .section{
        padding: 82px 0;
        background:#fff;
      }
      @media (max-width: 700px){
        .section{ padding: 62px 0; }
      }

      /* ===== Hero ===== */
      .hero{
        padding: 84px 0 54px;
        background:#fff;
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.05);
      }

      .heroInner{
        max-width: 900px;
      }

      .kicker{
        display:inline-flex;
        align-items:center;
        gap:10px;
        padding: 9px 13px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #fff;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.10);
        color: rgba(11,12,16,.78);
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: .2px;
      }
      .dot{
        width:8px;
        height:8px;
        border-radius:999px;
        background: rgba(11,12,16,.88);
      }

      h1{
        margin: 18px 0 12px;
        font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 64px);
        letter-spacing: -1.4px;
        line-height: 1.02;
        max-width: 11ch;
      }
      .sub{
        margin: 0;
        max-width: 60ch;
        font-size: clamp(16px, 1.55vw, 20px);
        color: rgba(11,12,16,.68);
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .ctaRow{
        margin-top: 22px;
        display:flex;
        gap: 12px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        align-items:center;
      }
      .btn{
        display:inline-flex;
        align-items:center;
        justify-content:center;
        gap:10px;
        height: 44px;
        padding: 0 16px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.12);
        background: #fff;
        color: rgba(11,12,16,.92);
        font-weight: 760;
        font-size: 14px;
        letter-spacing: .1px;
        transition: transform .18s var(--ease), background .18s var(--ease), border-color .18s var(--ease);
      }
      .btn:hover{
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        background: rgba(0,0,0,.02);
        border-color: rgba(0,0,0,.16);
      }
      .btnPrimary{
        border-color: transparent;
        background: var(--text);
        color: #fff;
      }
      .btnPrimary:hover{ background:#000; }
      .btn svg{
        width:16px;
        height:16px;
        stroke: currentColor;
        stroke-width:2.2;
        fill:none;
        stroke-linecap:round;
        stroke-linejoin:round;
      }

      /* ===== Media frames ===== */
      .float{
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: var(--rXL);
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        overflow:hidden;
      }
      .float.heroShot{
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
        margin-top: 34px;
        border-radius: 30px;
        background-image: url("/how-it-works/hero.jpg");
      }
      .float.stepShot{
        aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
      }
      .float.wideShot{
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
      }

      /* ===== Section headings ===== */
      .sectionHeader{
        display:flex;
        align-items:flex-end;
        justify-content:space-between;
        gap: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .sectionTitle{
        margin:0;
        font-size: clamp(22px, 2.2vw, 30px);
        letter-spacing:-.6px;
        line-height:1.08;
      }
      .sectionNote{
        margin:0;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 14.5px;
        line-height:1.45;
        max-width: 64ch;
      }

      /* ===== Steps ===== */
      .steps{
        display:grid;
        gap: 56px;
        margin-top: 26px;
      }
      .stepRow{
        display:grid;
        gap: 24px;
        align-items:center;
        padding: 24px 0;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.06);
      }
      .steps .stepRow:first-child{
        border-top: 0;
        padding-top: 0;
      }
      @media (min-width: 980px){
        .stepRow{
          grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(320px, .95fr);
          gap: 40px;
        }
        .stepRow.reverse{
          grid-template-columns: minmax(320px, .95fr) minmax(0, 1.05fr);
        }
        .stepRow.reverse .stepText{ order: 2; }
        .stepRow.reverse .stepMedia{ order: 1; }
      }

      .stepText{
        max-width: 560px;
      }
      .stepMedia{
        width:100%;
      }

      .stepNum{
        display:inline-flex;
        align-items:center;
        gap:10px;
        font-weight: 820;
        letter-spacing: .18px;
        color: rgba(11,12,16,.78);
        font-size: 13px;
      }
      .stepNum .pill{
        height: 26px;
        padding: 0 10px;
        display:inline-flex;
        align-items:center;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(0,0,0,.04);
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
        color: rgba(11,12,16,.86);
      }

      .stepTitle{
        margin: 12px 0 0;
        font-size: clamp(26px, 3.1vw, 42px);
        letter-spacing: -1px;
        line-height: 1.05;
      }
      .stepSub{
        margin: 14px 0 0;
        color: rgba(11,12,16,.68);
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 60ch;
      }
      .bullets{
        margin: 16px 0 0;
        padding-left: 18px;
        color: rgba(11,12,16,.64);
        font-size: 14.5px;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }
      .bullets li{ margin: 7px 0; }

      /* ===== Roles ===== */
      .roles{
        display:grid;
        gap: 22px;
        margin-top: 18px;
      }
      @media (min-width: 980px){
        .roles{ grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 38px; }
      }
      .roleCard{
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
        border-radius: var(--rM);
        padding: 22px;
        background:#fff;
      }
      .roleTitle{
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 18px;
        letter-spacing: -.3px;
      }
      .roleP{
        margin: 10px 0 0;
        color: rgba(11,12,16,.68);
        font-size: 15.5px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 60ch;
      }

      /* ===== FAQ ===== */
      .faqWrap{
        max-width: 860px;
      }
      details{
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.10);
        padding: 16px 0;
      }
      details:last-child{ border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.10); }
      summary{
        cursor:pointer;
        list-style:none;
        display:flex;
        align-items:center;
        justify-content:space-between;
        gap: 14px;
        font-weight: 780;
        letter-spacing: -.2px;
        font-size: 15px;
      }
      summary::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }
      .faqA{
        margin-top: 10px;
        color: rgba(11,12,16,.66);
        font-size: 14.8px;
        line-height: 1.65;
        max-width: 74ch;
      }
      .chev{
        width:34px;
        height:34px;
        border-radius:999px;
        display:grid;
        place-items:center;
        background: rgba(0,0,0,.04);
        border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
        flex: 0 0 auto;
      }
      .chev svg{
        width:16px;
        height:16px;
        stroke:#0b0c10;
        stroke-width:2.2;
        fill:none;
        transition: transform .18s var(--ease);
      }
      details[open] .chev svg{ transform: rotate(180deg); }

      .bottomCta{
        margin-top: 28px;
        display:flex;
        gap:12px;
        flex-wrap:wrap;
      }

      /* ===== Footer ===== */
      .footer{
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
        padding: 22px 0 40px;
        color: rgba(11,12,16,.62);
        font-size: 13px;
        display:flex;
        align-items:center;
        justify-content:space-between;
        gap: 14px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      .links{
        display:flex;
        gap: 14px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      .links a{ color: rgba(11,12,16,.62); }
      .links a:hover{ color: rgba(11,12,16,.90); }

      @media (max-width: 820px){
        .hero{
          padding: 68px 0 46px;
        }
        .float.heroShot{
          margin-top: 28px;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 560px){
        .topbarInner,
        .wrap{
          padding-left: 16px;
          padding-right: 16px;
        }
        h1{
          max-width: none;
        }
        .stepRow{
          gap: 18px;
        }
        .roleCard{
          padding: 18px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="topbarInner">
        <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="FLY Unlimited">
          <img class="mascot" src="/logo-alt.png" alt="FLY mascot" />
        </a>

        <nav class="nav" aria-label="Navigation">
          <a class="navBtn" href="/" aria-label="Home" title="Home">
            <img class="navIcon" src="/flyhome.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" />
          </a>

          <a class="navBtn active" href="/how-it-works/" aria-label="How it works" title="How it works">
            <img class="navIcon" src="/flyactive.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" />
          </a>

          <a class="navBtn" href="/info/" aria-label="Info" title="Info">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" />
              <path d="M12 10.6v6" />
              <path d="M12 7.4h.01" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero" aria-label="How it works hero">
      <div class="wrap heroInner">
        <div class="kicker"><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>How it works</div>

        <h1>From request to completion. In LiveTime.</h1>
        <p class="sub">
          Create a FLY, define the checklist, run it in LiveTime, attach proof where it belongs,
          and submit with a clean finish.
        </p>

        <div class="ctaRow" aria-label="Primary actions">
          <a class="btn btnPrimary" href={appStoreUrl} aria-label="App Store link">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14 7l-5 5 5 5"/><path d="M9 12h12"/></svg>
            Get the app
          </a>
          <a class="btn" href="#steps" aria-label="Jump to steps">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 5v14"/><path d="M5 12h14"/></svg>
            The steps
          </a>
          <a class="btn" href={"mailto:" + contactEmail} aria-label="Contact">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 6h16v12H4z"/><path d="m4 7 8 6 8-6"/></svg>
            Contact
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="float heroShot" role="img" aria-label="How it works hero image placeholder"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="steps" class="section" aria-label="Steps">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="sectionHeader">
          <div>
            <h2 class="sectionTitle">The flow, step by step.</h2>
            <p class="sectionNote">Simple by design. Everything stays organized, so completion is obvious.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="steps">
          <div class="stepRow">
            <div class="stepText">
              <div class="stepNum"><span class="pill">Step 1</span> Create</div>
              <div class="stepTitle">Create a FLY.</div>
              <p class="stepSub">
                Write a clear title, choose a category, and add location details if needed.
                Keep it specific so expectations are easy to understand from the start.
              </p>
              <ul class="bullets">
                <li>Use a short title that describes the outcome.</li>
                <li>Add timing or location constraints up front.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="stepMedia">
              <div
                class="float stepShot"
                style="background-image: url('/how-it-works/step-1.jpg');"
                role="img"
                aria-label="Step 1 image placeholder"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="stepRow reverse">
            <div class="stepText">
              <div class="stepNum"><span class="pill">Step 2</span> Checklist</div>
              <div class="stepTitle">Define what “done” means.</div>
              <p class="stepSub">
                Add checklist items for materials, key information, and goals.
                This becomes the shared definition of completion for everyone involved.
              </p>
              <ul class="bullets">
                <li>Three to seven items is usually the sweet spot.</li>
                <li>End with a clear finish-line goal.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="stepMedia">
              <div
                class="float stepShot"
                style="background-image: url('/how-it-works/step-2.jpg');"
                role="img"
                aria-label="Step 2 image placeholder"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="stepRow">
            <div class="stepText">
              <div class="stepNum"><span class="pill">Step 3</span> LiveTime</div>
              <div class="stepTitle">Start LiveTime.</div>
              <p class="stepSub">
                LiveTime is where the work happens. Resume anytime, message in context,
                and keep progress tied directly to the FLY instead of scattered across threads.
              </p>
              <ul class="bullets">
                <li>Use Message to keep conversation tied to the job.</li>
                <li>Use Directions when location matters.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="stepMedia">
              <div
                class="float stepShot"
                style="background-image: url('/how-it-works/step-3.jpg');"
                role="img"
                aria-label="Step 3 image placeholder"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="stepRow reverse">
            <div class="stepText">
              <div class="stepNum"><span class="pill">Step 4</span> Proof</div>
              <div class="stepTitle">Attach proof where it belongs.</div>
              <p class="stepSub">
                Add photos, files, and notes inside each checklist item.
                Review stays clean because nothing is buried or out of place.
              </p>
              <ul class="bullets">
                <li>Put media inside the relevant checklist item thread.</li>
                <li>Use short notes to explain what changed.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="stepMedia">
              <div
                class="float stepShot"
                style="background-image: url('/how-it-works/step-4.jpg');"
                role="img"
                aria-label="Step 4 image placeholder"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="stepRow">
            <div class="stepText">
              <div class="stepNum"><span class="pill">Step 5</span> Submit</div>
              <div class="stepTitle">Submit with confidence.</div>
              <p class="stepSub">
                When goals are complete, submit the FLY. The author reviews the LiveTime trail
                and finalizes the work with everything already organized for review.
              </p>
              <ul class="bullets">
                <li>Submission is fast because the structure is already there.</li>
                <li>Any questions stay tied to the job context.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="stepMedia">
              <div
                class="float stepShot"
                style="background-image: url('/how-it-works/step-5.jpg');"
                role="img"
                aria-label="Step 5 image placeholder"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" aria-label="Roles">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="sectionHeader">
          <div>
            <h2 class="sectionTitle">Two roles, one workflow.</h2>
            <p class="sectionNote">Whether you’re the author or performer, the flow stays simple.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="roles">
          <div class="roleCard">
            <h3 class="roleTitle">If you’re the Author</h3>
            <p class="roleP">
              Create the FLY, define the checklist, and review the LiveTime trail on submission.
              Approve when it’s complete, with proof already organized in the right places.
            </p>
            <ul class="bullets">
              <li>Create and clarify expectations.</li>
              <li>Message in context when needed.</li>
              <li>Review proof by checklist item.</li>
              <li>Finalize smoothly.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="roleCard">
            <h3 class="roleTitle">If you’re the Performer</h3>
            <p class="roleP">
              Start LiveTime when you’re ready, post proof inside each step, and submit when complete.
              The job stays readable and easy to finish well.
            </p>
            <ul class="bullets">
              <li>Work step by step.</li>
              <li>Attach proof where it belongs.</li>
              <li>Submit when goals are done.</li>
              <li>Keep messaging tied to the FLY.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="float wideShot"
          style="margin-top:34px; background-image: url('/how-it-works/roles.jpg');"
          role="img"
          aria-label="Roles image placeholder"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" aria-label="FAQ">
      <div class="wrap faqWrap">
        <div class="sectionHeader">
          <div>
            <h2 class="sectionTitle">FAQ</h2>
            <p class="sectionNote">Short answers, designed to be clear.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <details>
          <summary>
            What is LiveTime?
            <span class="chev" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faqA">
            LiveTime is the work space for a FLY, where progress, proof, and messages stay tied to the checklist.
            It keeps everything organized and easy to review.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details>
          <summary>
            Why attach proof inside checklist items?
            <span class="chev" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faqA">
            Because it removes the usual “where is that photo or file?” problem. Proof stays with the step it belongs to,
            so review becomes fast and obvious.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details>
          <summary>
            Can I message inside a FLY?
            <span class="chev" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faqA">
            Yes. Messaging stays tied to the job so you do not lose context or mix conversations.
          </div>
        </details>

        <details>
          <summary>
            What happens after Submit?
            <span class="chev" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/></svg></span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faqA">
            The author reviews the LiveTime trail and finalizes the FLY. If questions come up, they stay tied to that same context.
          </div>
        </details>

        <div class="bottomCta">
          <a class="btn btnPrimary" href={appStoreUrl} aria-label="Get the app">Get the app</a>
          <a class="btn" href={"mailto:" + contactEmail} aria-label="Email support">Email support</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="wrap footer" aria-label="Footer">
      <div>© 2026 {siteName}</div>
      <div class="links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/info/">Contact</a>
        <a href="/terms/">Terms</a>
        <a href="/privacy/">Privacy</a>
        <a href={"mailto:" + contactEmail}>hello@fly-unlimited.com</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
